data: The event "Product Feature Brainstorming" was designed to generate new product feature ideas for NextGen Labs.
The event "Product Feature Brainstorming" covered discussion topics including heatmap analytics ideas, interactive journey mapping, backend complexity concerns, and a phased rollout approach.
The event "Product Feature Brainstorming" resulted in key decisions to implement a phased rollout and to focus development on heatmap visualization and real-time collaboration features.
The event "Product Feature Brainstorming" produced action items to prototype the heatmap module and to draft a technical specification.
The event "Product Feature Brainstorming" involved selection of top feature concepts—real-time collaboration, heatmap visualization, and phased integration—through team voting.
